title: Gurnard Soup
content:
Gurnard Soup are a category of item. It can be cooked in The Delectable Dab Kitchen in Hopeport using the Chef profession. Recipes for the Chef profession can be found in the Chef Recipe Book. Gurnard Soups can be sold to Head Chef.


 * Yellowtail Gurnard Soup
 * Bigeye Gurnard Soup
 * Blackfin Gurnard Soup
 * Shiny Gurnard Soup
 * Torpedo Gurnard Soup
 * Grand Gurnard Soup
